  brain/groq-mapper.js                — DOM-first element resolution + position-enriched prompts
  brain/recovery-engine.js            — 3-tier retry + disambiguation + user confirmation
  brain/guidance-state.js             — GuidanceSession (single source of truth) + SyncController

DELETE FILES (3):
  utils/context-engine.js             — duplicate DOM scanner
  utils/teacher-prompt.js             — prompt generator (replaced by normalizer)
  utils/step-parser.js                — bracket-hint parser (replaced by normalizer)

KEPT (previously planned for deletion):
  utils/intent-profiler.js            — drives Page Validation + matching strategy
  utils/screenshot-manager.js         — vision fallback ONLY (not default, invoked by recovery)
  content/ai-content.js               — background injection for clarification + voice queries

MAJOR MODIFICATIONS (7):
  background/service-worker.js        — pipeline orchestration + session ownership + VOICE_QUERY handler
  content/cursor-guide.js             — CompletionValidator + outcome reporting + listening-mode visualizer
  content/content.js                  — MutationObserver (structural) + SESSION_STATE_UPDATE consumer
